{
  "stem": "935.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The same night, I looked out this little cubby hole.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "At night, it was very, very eerie.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was very quiet, usually.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The street was very empty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And there, I heard-- it must have been past midnight-- trucks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And when you hear nothing, the sound of moving trucks in the stillness is very dominating.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And it was the children from the Warsaw ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This was their last journey.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They were all ended up in the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] From then on, I never looked out again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Never again.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "My friend Reina, of course, got typhus and died there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Through Ilse, I was able to get to see her in the revier, in the hospital, at all.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I remember I brought her soup that didn't stink, but she was no longer-- she was in a sheet with somebody who was already dead.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was so strange, like, like this dead girl, whoever she was, was waiting for her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They were in the same sheet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And the other strange thing is that you really don't mourn anyone who dies in a camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Not if the pain is too much, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[CRYING] I think you just wonder where God is in all of this, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] especially for someone like Reina who did believe in him.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You wonder, and you go home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] The other thing you have to watch there is you get these sores, which is, as I learned later, lack of vitamins, lack of food.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It's very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "It starts with-- you know, normally, you get a little scratch and it heals.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But that doesn't heal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "It becomes bigger, and bigger, and it becomes a big hole.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
